12:39.818 --> 12:46.645
He suffered in his body on our behalf, defeated sin at the cross, the grave could not hold him.

12:47.566 --> 12:52.731
He rose again and sits at the right hand of God, all in submission to him.

12:54.393 --> 12:55.634
